N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 3.32 - Admission of public schools to the university

State Regulations

All public elementary, middle and secondary schools in the

State of New York, other than charter schools, shall be registered by the Board
of Regents pursuant to the regulations of the commissioner and all public
schools shall be deemed admitted to the University of the State of New

York. Notes
